snippet.title: One More Dash game trailer (From the creators of One More Line & OTTTD)
snippet.description:
Available for FREE to the IOS App store & Google Play.
https://geo.itunes.apple.com/au/app/one-more-dash/id985923564?mt=8&uo=6&at=10lcrI
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.smgstudio.omd

Dash - Collect - Die - Repeat.
A deceptively simple game about timing. 
From the creators of One More Line

Follow us on https://twitter.com/smgstudio | https://www.facebook.com/SMGStudio 

One More Line available now
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4x3Vp5MBooM

Original music by Jared Underwood/ Batterie http://batterie.com.au/
